♪ <i>Your love from me</i> ♪

2005
02:36:00,417 --> 02:36:05,333
♪ <i>Would I be fool
to ever leave you, dear?</i> ♪

2006
02:36:05,417 --> 02:36:11,542
♪ <i>And a fool I'd ever be</i> ♪

2007
