♪ <i>That's what you are</i> ♪

2011
02:36:58,917 --> 02:37:01,208
♪ <i>Heaven</i> ♪

2012
02:37:01,292 --> 02:37:05,208
♪ <i>And heaven alone can take</i> ♪

2013
02:37:05,292 --> 02:37:09,208
♪ <i>Your love from me</i> ♪

2014
02:37:09,292 --> 02:37:14,542
♪ <i>But I'd be fool
To ever leave you, dear</i> ♪

2015
02:37:14,625 --> 02:37:20,167
♪ <i>And a fool I'd never be</i> ♪

2016
02:37:31,458 --> 02:37:32,875
Mr. Tóth?

2017
02:37:38,000 --> 02:37:40,250
It's time we return
to our quarters.

2018
02:37:50,917 --> 02:37:54,500
Orazio has very kindly
offered us

2019
02:37:54,583 --> 02:37:57,583
a place to sleep
for the night.

2020
02:38:04,667 --> 02:38:06,042
Mr. Tóth?

2021
02:38:22,333 --> 02:38:24,375
What have you done
to yourself?

2022
02:38:33,000 --> 02:38:34,917
It's a shame seeing how...

2023
02:38:36,667 --> 02:38:38,625
your people treat themselves.

2024
02:38:41,125 --> 02:38:42,750
If you resent
your persecution,

2025
02:38:42,833 --> 02:38:44,833
why then do you make
of yourself

2026
02:38:44,917 --> 02:38:46,458
such an easy target?

2027
02:38:47,708 --> 02:38:49,417
Hmm?

2028
02:38:50,792 --> 02:38:52,875
if you act as a loafer,

2029
02:38:54,208 --> 02:38:57,000
living off hand-outs...

2030
02:38:58,542 --> 02:39:00,250
a societal leech,

2031
02:39:01,625 --> 02:39:03,375
how can you...

2032
02:39:03,458 --> 02:39:06,917
how can you rightfully expect
a different result?

2033
02:39:10,292 --> 02:39:13,250
You...
You have so much potential.

2034
02:39:15,583 --> 02:39:17,292
Yet you squander it.

2035
02:39:29,208 --> 02:39:31,625
Get it out. Let it out.

2036
02:39:34,417 --> 02:39:37,000
Let it out. It's all right.

2037
02:39:42,792 --> 02:39:44,458
It's all right.

2038
02:39:48,500 --> 02:39:50,875
Who do you think you are?

2039
02:39:50,958 --> 02:39:52,583
Who do you think you are?

2040
02:39:52,667 --> 02:39:54,667
You think you're special?

2041
02:39:56,292 --> 02:39:58,792
You think you...

2042
02:39:58,875 --> 02:40:02,500
You just float directly above
all those you encounter

2043
02:40:02,583 --> 02:40:05,000
because you're beautiful, huh?

2044
