Because you're educated?

2045
02:40:13,000 --> 02:40:14,542
You're just a tramp.

2046
02:40:14,625 --> 02:40:17,417
You're a lady of the night.

2047
02:40:17,500 --> 02:40:19,750
You're just a lady
of the night.

2048
02:40:43,250 --> 02:40:50,250
♪ <i>That's what you are</i> ♪

2049
02:41:29,792 --> 02:41:31,792
You were in quite a state
last night.

2050
02:41:34,125 --> 02:41:36,042
Orazio carried you to bed.

2051
02:41:42,458 --> 02:41:45,833
It's a four-hour train
to the airport in Fiumicino.

2052
02:41:47,208 --> 02:41:49,583
So you'll have time
for a rest.

2053
02:41:52,458 --> 02:41:55,417
I hope your stomach is not
too sensitive on airplanes.

2054
02:44:45,083 --> 02:44:47,292
You see this, above us?

2055
02:44:47,375 --> 02:44:48,833
Measure the same distance

2056
02:44:48,917 --> 02:44:52,250
of three or perhaps
four inches between flats,

2057
02:44:52,333 --> 02:44:55,750
and place each modular section
apart by that same distance.

2058
02:44:56,583 --> 02:44:58,375
Then what do we do
with the gaps?

2059
02:45:00,833 --> 02:45:05,917
We insert a thick sheet
of glass between the panels

2060
02:45:06,000 --> 02:45:08,000
to let the light in
from above.

2061
02:45:10,667 --> 02:45:12,125
Give me some time
to think about it

2062
02:45:12,208 --> 02:45:13,542
and I'll come back to you.

2063
02:45:13,625 --> 02:45:15,000
Twenty-two.

2064
02:45:15,083 --> 02:45:16,917
- Twenty-three.
- What's going on here?

2065
02:45:17,000 --> 02:45:18,625
Twenty-four.

2066
02:45:18,708 --> 02:45:20,458
Twenty-five.

2067
02:45:20,542 --> 02:45:22,042
Twenty-six.

2068
02:45:22,125 --> 02:45:23,750
Twenty-seven.

2069
02:45:23,833 --> 02:45:25,542
Twenty-eight.

2070
02:45:25,625 --> 02:45:27,500
Twenty-nine.

2071
02:45:27,583 --> 02:45:29,167
Thirty.

2072
02:45:29,250 --> 02:45:31,000
- Thirty-one.
- Stop it right now!

2073
02:45:31,083 --> 02:45:33,625
- Thirty-two.
- Stop it! Stop it right now!

2074
02:45:33,708 --> 02:45:36,417
You, what is your name, huh?

2075
02:45:36,500 --> 02:45:39,208
Are you stupid? You want
to pull this whole thing down?

2076
02:45:39,292 --> 02:45:40,792
Want to get them all killed?

2077
02:45:40,875 --> 02:45:44,208
Your childish show-boating
puts everyone here at risk!

2078
02:45:44,292 --> 02:45:46,125
Do you hear me?

2079
02:45:46,208 --> 02:45:47,875
Are you thick? Are you lame?

2080
02:45:47,958 --> 02:45:51,083
Gordon, can you get him
to stop shouting at everyone?

2081
02:45:52,917 --> 02:45:54,167
I will.

2082
02:45:56,292 --> 02:45:58,167
You report
to the subcontractor.

2083
02:45:58,250 --> 02:46:00,667
You tell him
that you've been let go.

2084
02:46:03,375 --> 02:46:04,667
- Get out of here!
- Hey!

2085
02:46:04,750 --> 02:46:06,333
What's wrong with you, László?

2086
02:46:06,417 --> 02:46:07,750
You kicked that boy.

2087
02:46:08,917 --> 02:46:10,292
Stay out of it, Gordon.

2088
02:46:11,458 --> 02:46:14,667
- What's wrong with you?
- Stay out of it.

2089
02:46:14,750 --> 02:46:16,792
Stay out of it,
or you can go with him!

2090
02:46:17,833 --> 02:46:20,792
You shout at me again
and you'll be sorry.

2091
02:46:23,375 --> 02:46:25,208
You too! You go!

2092
02:46:25,292 --> 02:46:27,167
Go! Get out of here.

2093
02:46:28,708 --> 02:46:30,208
Get out of here.

2094
02:46:32,708 --> 02:46:35,500
You think
I am playing games with you?

2095
02:46:39,667 --> 02:46:42,208
Let's go. Let's go.

2096
02:46:42,292 --> 02:46:44,083
I only just arrived.

2097
02:46:45,500 --> 02:46:47,750
- Mr. Tóth.
- Oh, God.

2098
02:46:47,833 --> 02:46:49,042
Mr. Tóth, we need to talk

2099
02:46:49,125 --> 02:46:50,250
about these May-June
cost reports.

2100
02:46:50,333 --> 02:46:52,542
Not today, Jimmy, not today.

2101
02:46:52,625 --> 02:46:54,292
You can't keep
walking away from me

2102
02:46:54,375 --> 02:46:56,000
every time I step into a room.

2103
02:46:56,083 --> 02:46:58,417
This is not a room, Jim.

2104
02:46:58,500 --> 02:47:00,875
Honey, did I introduce you
to Jim Simpson?

2105
02:47:00,958 --> 02:47:03,125
Jim is the boss's lapdog

2106
02:47:03,208 --> 02:47:07,333
and architectural consultant
extraordinaire!

2107
02:47:07,417 --> 02:47:10,000
Jim designed a hotel
in Stamford.

2108
02:47:10,083 --> 02:47:11,750
László, that's enough.

2109
02:47:11,833 --> 02:47:14,125
Come on, Jimmy, there must be
an unpaid parking meter

2110
02:47:14,208 --> 02:47:16,583
around here somewhere, huh?

2111
02:47:16,667 --> 02:47:18,167
Be vigilant!

2112
02:47:19,542 --> 02:47:21,125
Keep your eyes peeled!

2113
02:47:23,667 --> 02:47:26,042
What is it, huh?

2114
02:47:26,792 --> 02:47:30,333
It was unnecessary how
you treated that boy, is all.

2115
02:47:32,000 --> 02:47:34,625
Their safety is my priority.

2116
02:47:34,708 --> 02:47:37,083
It is not what you said
to that young man, it is how.

2117
02:47:37,167 --> 02:47:39,625
Gordon?
Don't even get me started.

2118
02:47:39,708 --> 02:47:42,292
Do you want to wait around
for another few years

2119
02:47:42,375 --> 02:47:46,792
for another lawsuit
to resolve itself?

2120
02:47:46,875 --> 02:47:50,042
Hmm? I am sick of it.

2121
02:47:50,125 --> 02:47:52,083
Sick! Do you hear me?

2122
02:47:53,333 --> 02:47:55,125
I finish this
or we are finished.

2123
02:47:55,208 --> 02:47:58,000
Speak for yourself.
I am not finished.

2124
02:47:58,083 --> 02:47:59,833
Living with you is impossible.

2125
02:47:59,917 --> 02:48:01,750
You've become
a selfish old bastard

2126
02:48:01,833 --> 02:48:02,917
right before my very eyes.

2127
02:48:03,000 --> 02:48:05,042
Don't say something
you'll regret in the morning.

2128
02:48:05,125 --> 02:48:08,292
Do you want to kill us?

2129
02:48:08,375 --> 02:48:10,500
I'd get out of the car
and march all the way

2130
02:48:10,583 --> 02:48:14,000
back to Manhattan if I could,
you egotistic scoundrel!

2131
02:48:15,042 --> 02:48:18,083
There is no reason
for me to be here.

2132
02:48:18,167 --> 02:48:22,292
I'm here for you. I could do
my ridiculous job anywhere!

2133
02:48:22,917 --> 02:48:24,417
Do you think
I went to university

2134
02:48:24,500 --> 02:48:26,292
to write about lipsticks?

2135
02:48:27,125 --> 02:48:28,583
Shame on you!

2136
02:48:28,667 --> 02:48:32,375
We came here because it was
our only option!

2137
02:48:35,000 --> 02:48:38,083
- Attila was here...
- Who you refuse to see!

2138
02:48:38,167 --> 02:48:41,125
Ask him about that! Ask him.

2139
02:48:42,083 --> 02:48:45,667
Did he tell you he kicked me
to the street like a dog?

2140
02:48:45,750 --> 02:48:47,042
Did he?

2141
02:48:47,125 --> 02:48:50,167
His bitch, bitch wife
accused me

2142
02:48:50,250 --> 02:48:51,792
of making a pass at her.

2143
02:48:51,875 --> 02:48:54,625
- You would never do that.
- I did not do that.

2144
02:48:54,708 --> 02:48:56,625
Then why would she say
such a thing?

2145
02:48:56,708 --> 02:48:58,333
Because
they do not want us here.

2146
02:48:58,417 --> 02:49:00,667
Of course
Attila wants us here.

2147
02:49:00,750 --> 02:49:02,625
- Not Attila.
- Then who do you mean?

2148
02:49:02,708 --> 02:49:06,000
The people here.
They do not want us here.

2149
02:49:08,458 --> 02:49:11,875
Audrey,
Attila's Catholic wife,

2150
02:49:11,958 --> 02:49:13,667
does not want us here!

2151
02:49:14,542 --> 02:49:16,375
She does not want us here!

2152
02:49:21,458 --> 02:49:23,000
We are nothing.

2153
02:49:26,375 --> 02:49:27,917
We are worse than nothing.

2154
02:49:29,583 --> 02:49:31,083
You poor man.

2155
02:49:32,708 --> 02:49:34,375
My poor husband.

2156
02:49:37,542 --> 02:49:38,583
What...

2157
02:49:40,000 --> 02:49:41,833
What has been robbed of you?

2158
02:49:47,667 --> 02:49:49,458
- Zsótia!
- Shh.

2159
02:49:49,542 --> 02:49:51,125
- Zsófia!
- She's not here, darling.

2160
02:49:51,208 --> 02:49:52,375
She's not here.

2161
02:49:52,458 --> 02:49:54,958
- Zsó...
- Sorry I upset you. Please.

2162
02:49:55,042 --> 02:49:59,458
Get me my pills.

2163
02:49:59,542 --> 02:50:02,542
It's too much.

2164
02:50:02,625 --> 02:50:05,917
I'm in pain!
I'm close to death!

2165
02:50:12,083 --> 02:50:13,750
Darling?

2166
02:50:13,833 --> 02:50:16,542
There is only a pill
cut in halves.

2167
02:50:16,625 --> 02:50:18,667
Do you have more
in your purse?

2168
02:50:18,750 --> 02:50:21,250
I can't.

2169
02:50:21,333 --> 02:50:23,083
Darling.

2170
02:50:23,167 --> 02:50:24,208
Take this, please.

2171
02:50:24,292 --> 02:50:25,750
Do you have more
in your purse?

2172
02:50:27,542 --> 02:50:28,667
No?

2173
02:50:30,083 --> 02:50:32,167
This is too much.

2174
02:50:32,250 --> 02:50:33,792
What will I do?

2175
02:50:33,875 --> 02:50:36,500
The pain.
This is too much, László.

2176
02:50:36,583 --> 02:50:39,750
Shh.

2177
02:50:53,208 --> 02:50:55,875
Darling,
I will find something.

2178
02:51:00,208 --> 02:51:03,708
Darling, come on.
Shh. Shh.

2179
02:51:06,958 --> 02:51:09,208
It's what they gave me
on the boat

2180
02:51:09,292 --> 02:51:11,167
for my broken face.

2181
02:51:15,958 --> 02:51:17,667
It'll help you feel better.

2182
02:51:17,750 --> 02:51:20,333
Just listen to my voice, dear.

2183
02:51:22,375 --> 02:51:24,583
That's it.
Just listen to my voice.

2184
02:51:26,708 --> 02:51:29,042
Listen to my voice.

2185
02:51:30,167 --> 02:51:31,542
There you go.

2186
02:51:32,875 --> 02:51:34,833
Listen to my voice.

2187
02:51:36,208 --> 02:51:38,417
There you go. Shh.

2188
02:51:40,000 --> 02:51:42,083
Listen to my voice.

2189
02:51:42,167 --> 02:51:43,625
Good, my dear.

2190
02:51:45,708 --> 02:51:47,042
There you go.

2191
02:51:49,000 --> 02:51:50,417
There you go.

2192
02:51:58,667 --> 02:51:59,792
Good.

2193
02:52:02,000 --> 02:52:04,458
Listen to my voice, darling.

2194
02:52:11,792 --> 02:52:15,042
Do... Do you have more?

2195
02:52:52,000 --> 02:52:53,375
Keep going.

2196
02:53:01,708 --> 02:53:03,042
Harder.

2197
02:54:43,708 --> 02:54:45,000
Toilet.

2198
02:54:52,542 --> 02:54:53,750
Toilet.

2199
02:54:55,125 --> 02:54:56,417
Yes, dear.

2200
02:54:58,917 --> 02:54:59,917
Yes.

2201
02:55:05,167 --> 02:55:07,417
Up. Come, my dear.

2202
02:55:07,500 --> 02:55:09,458
Oh. Yeah.

2203
02:55:09,542 --> 02:55:10,917
Come on.

2204
02:55:11,000 --> 02:55:12,500
Come...

2205
02:55:15,750 --> 02:55:17,833
Oh. All right?

2206
02:55:17,917 --> 02:55:19,375
I'll wait outside.

2207
02:55:20,042 --> 02:55:22,708
Okay? You tell me
when you need me.

2208
02:55:47,208 --> 02:55:48,375
Darling?

2209
02:55:51,125 --> 02:55:52,583
Have you finished?

2210
02:55:57,125 --> 02:55:59,000
Darling, can I come in?

2211
02:56:02,375 --> 02:56:04,875
Darling? Erzsébet?

2212
02:56:04,958 --> 02:56:07,792
Help. Help me. Help.

2213
02:56:07,875 --> 02:56:09,375
I need a gurney,
a stretcher!

2214
02:56:09,458 --> 02:56:10,458
Anything! Anything!

2215
02:56:10,542 --> 02:56:12,625
Help me.
Help, my wife is dying.

2216
02:56:12,708 --> 02:56:14,458
She'll be all right.
Okay, okay, okay.

2217
02:56:14,542 --> 02:56:16,875
- My wife is dying.
- She'll be all right.

2218
02:56:16,958 --> 02:56:18,875
Quickly, quickly, quickly!

2219
02:56:18,958 --> 02:56:21,125
I know my wife,
she's dying.

2220
02:56:59,208 --> 02:57:01,458
Last night, I met God.

2221
02:57:02,625 --> 02:57:06,083
He granted me permission
to call Him by His name.

2222
02:57:08,708 --> 02:57:11,167
It is not the first time
we have met.

2223
02:57:15,042 --> 02:57:17,708
What did you do to me,
my László?

2224
02:57:21,000 --> 02:57:23,000
It was an accident.

2225
02:57:28,375 --> 02:57:31,375
Do you remember everything
you confessed to me

2226
02:57:31,458 --> 02:57:33,208
at home in our bed?

2227
02:57:39,458 --> 02:57:42,375
Oh, you needn't be ashamed,
my darling.

2228
02:57:44,208 --> 02:57:45,750
The harm done unto us

2229
02:57:45,833 --> 02:57:48,625
was done only
to our physical bodies.

2230
02:57:50,458 --> 02:57:51,958
You were right.

2231
02:57:54,167 --> 02:57:56,250
This place is rotten.

2232
02:57:57,625 --> 02:58:00,250
The landscape,
the food we eat,

2233
02:58:01,042 --> 02:58:03,292
this whole country is rotten.

2234
02:58:06,375 --> 02:58:08,375
I'm going to Israel

2235
02:58:08,458 --> 02:58:10,667
to be with Zsófia
and her child.

2236
02:58:12,417 --> 02:58:15,042
I want to become
the grandmother to her

2237
02:58:15,125 --> 02:58:17,708
that she will otherwise
never encounter.

2238
02:58:24,792 --> 02:58:26,500
Come home with me.

2239
02:58:32,625 --> 02:58:34,375
Come home with me.

2240
02:58:38,250 --> 02:58:39,917
I will follow you.

2241
02:58:42,917 --> 02:58:45,333
I will follow you until I die.

2242
02:59:52,542 --> 02:59:54,542
Mrs. Tóth.

2243
02:59:54,625 --> 02:59:57,167
You're standing.
How lovely to see.

2244
02:59:57,250 --> 02:59:59,625
- Do you need a hand?
- I'm all right, thank you.

2245
02:59:59,708 --> 03:00:01,417
Is Mr. Tóth here as well?

2246
03:00:01,500 --> 03:00:03,750
- Just me, I'm afraid.
- Oh.

2247
03:00:03,833 --> 03:00:06,042
To what do we owe
the pleasure?

2248
03:00:06,125 --> 03:00:08,042
Is your father in?

2249
03:00:08,125 --> 03:00:10,583
Sure. We were just
sitting down for dinner.

2250
03:00:10,667 --> 03:00:12,917
No trouble at all,
I'm happy to wait

2251
03:00:13,000 --> 03:00:14,292
until you're all finished.

2252
03:00:15,625 --> 03:00:17,000
Don't be silly.

2253
03:00:17,083 --> 03:00:18,833
I'll ask the kitchen
to fix you a plate.

2254
03:00:19,750 --> 03:00:23,042
You're kind, Maggie.
Thank you.

2255
03:00:24,167 --> 03:00:26,292
Follow me.

2256
03:00:30,333 --> 03:00:32,750
You can finally meet
my fiancé.

2257
03:00:36,792 --> 03:00:39,083
Are you sure
you don't need a hand?

2258
03:00:39,167 --> 03:00:40,250
I'm fine.

2259
03:00:43,333 --> 03:00:45,167
Mrs. Tóth.

2260
03:00:45,250 --> 03:00:46,667
You're up on your feet.

2261
03:00:46,750 --> 03:00:49,292
Please, sit.

2262
03:00:50,417 --> 03:00:51,750
Where's László?

2263
03:00:54,167 --> 03:00:56,083
He's caught a flu.

2264
03:00:56,792 --> 03:00:58,583
He's recovering at home.

2265
03:00:58,667 --> 03:01:00,708
Well, that explains it.

2266
03:01:00,792 --> 03:01:02,792
Jim Simpson mentioned
he hadn't been on site

2267
03:01:02,875 --> 03:01:04,208
since last Friday.

2268
03:01:04,292 --> 03:01:06,542
- Shame.
- Yes.

2269
03:01:07,250 --> 03:01:09,458
A terrible shame.

2270
03:01:09,542 --> 03:01:11,042
It's going around.

2271
03:01:11,667 --> 03:01:14,042
Please. Sit down.

2272
03:01:14,125 --> 03:01:15,833
I'm fine to stand.

2273
03:01:17,667 --> 03:01:19,167
Fine to stand?

2274
03:01:21,000 --> 03:01:22,792
Is something wrong, Mrs. Tóth?

2275
03:01:25,042 --> 03:01:29,083
Yes.
Something is wrong.

2276
03:01:32,083 --> 03:01:34,750
I have come tonight
to tell you something

2277
03:01:34,833 --> 03:01:37,667
that is going to be
very difficult to hear.

2278
03:01:40,000 --> 03:01:41,833
For you people, too.

2279
03:01:43,958 --> 03:01:48,750
I don't know you, but it will
be difficult for you to hear.

2280
03:01:49,750 --> 03:01:51,458
If this
is a professional matter,

2281
03:01:51,542 --> 03:01:54,250
then perhaps you and I should
talk in the other room.

2282
03:01:56,667 --> 03:01:58,958
Your father is a rapist.

2283
03:02:02,333 --> 03:02:03,833
Excuse me?

2284
03:02:06,500 --> 03:02:08,083
Whatever this is
supposed to be,

2285
03:02:08,167 --> 03:02:09,458
I don't like it.

2286
03:02:10,583 --> 03:02:12,542
I'm calling your husband
to come and fetch you.

2287
03:02:12,625 --> 03:02:15,833
Your father is an evil rapist.

2288
03:02:16,833 --> 03:02:19,458
Daddy,
what is she talking about?

2289
03:02:19,542 --> 03:02:20,958
Look at him.

2290
03:02:22,083 --> 03:02:24,000
He cannot say anything.

2291
03:02:27,167 --> 03:02:29,333
Did something happen
between you and Mrs. Tóth?

2292
03:02:29,417 --> 03:02:32,042
- It wasn't me.
- That's enough!

2293
03:02:33,083 --> 03:02:36,625
You come in here making vague,
laughable accusations.

2294
03:02:36,708 --> 03:02:39,083
I want you out of our house
this instant.

2295
03:02:39,167 --> 03:02:42,750
Tell them
what you did to my husband.

2296
03:02:43,708 --> 03:02:45,958
Tell them what you did.

2297
03:02:50,625 --> 03:02:52,000
Your husband is sick.

2298
03:02:53,167 --> 03:02:55,833
He's alcoholic. Drug-addicted.

2299
03:02:56,833 --> 03:03:01,000
I don't know why he wishes
to hurt me, to humiliate me.

2300
03:03:02,333 --> 03:03:04,417
I have offered him
nothing but kindness.

2301
03:03:05,750 --> 03:03:09,292
He's a sick, senile old dog

2302
03:03:10,458 --> 03:03:12,917
and when dogs get sick,
they...

2303
